data.description: Welcome home to this lovely 5 bedroom home! Fresh paint throughout, updated kitchen and flooring.  Gather in the very large family room or enjoy the outdoors on the back deck. With bedrooms and a full bath on the main floor, first floor living is easily offered if desired. The full basement has nature stone flooring. This property boasts both, a garage and shed for use. Comes with a 1 year home warranty for the new owner! Updated kitchen, new flooring, new roof (front and garage).
